'''金融區'''（{{lang-en|Financial District}}），又稱 '''FiDi'''<ref>{{cite news|last1=Couzzo|first1=Steve|title=FiDi Soaring High|url=http://nypost.com/2007/04/25/fidi-soaring-high/|accessdate=December 3, 2014|publisher=New York Post|date=April 25, 2007|quote=The Financial District is over. So is the “Wall Street area.” But say hello to FiDi, the coinage of major downtown landlord Kent Swig, who decided it’s time to humanize the old F.D. with an easily remembered, fun-sounding acronym.|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204212/http://nypost.com/2007/04/25/fidi-soaring-high/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]的一個{{link-en|曼哈頓境內地區列表|List of Manhattan neighborhoods|地區}}，位於曼哈頓南端，集中了眾多金融機構的辦事處和總部，包括[[紐約證券交易所|紐約證券交易所]]和[[紐約聯邦儲備銀行|紐約聯邦儲備銀行]]，是紐約成為世界金融和經濟中心的重要源動力<ref name=EconomicallyPowerful2015>{{cite web|url=http://www.citylab.com/work/2015/03/sorry-london-new-york-is-the-worlds-most-economically-powerful-city/386315/|title=Sorry, London: New York Is the World's Most Economically Powerful City|author=Richard Florida|publisher=The Atlantic Monthly Group|date=March 3, 2015|accessdate=March 25, 2015|quote=Our new ranking puts the Big Apple firmly on top.|archive-date=2015-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314002727/http://www.citylab.com/work/2015/03/sorry-london-new-york-is-the-worlds-most-economically-powerful-city/386315/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WorldEconomicAndFinancialSuperCenter>{{cite web|url=http://articles.businessinsider.com/2011-07-31/markets/30005560_1_cities-economic-output-gdp|title=Top 8 Cities by GDP: China vs. The U.S.|quote=For instance, Shanghai, the largest Chinese city with the highest economic production, and a fast-growing global financial hub, is far from matching or surpassing New York, the largest city in the U.S. and the economic and financial super center of the world.|publisher=Business Insider, Inc|date=July 31, 2011|accessdate=March 25, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130205063107/http://articles.businessinsider.com/2011-07-31/markets/30005560_1_cities-economic-output-gdp|archivedate=2013年2月5日}}<br/>{{cite web|url=http://www.philippineairlines.com/news-and-events/pal-advises-passengers-come-airport-early-2/|title=PAL sets introductory fares to New York|publisher=Philippine Airlines|accessdate=March 25, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113111435/http://www.philippineairlines.com/news-and-events/pal-advises-passengers-come-airport-early-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-11-24/new-york-boosts-lead-on-london-as-leading-finance-center.html|title=New York Boosts Lead on London as Leading Finance Center|author=John Glover|publisher=Bloomberg L.P|date=November 23, 2014|accessdate=March 25, 2015|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112154508/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-11-24/new-york-boosts-lead-on-london-as-leading-finance-center.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/world-news/ubs-may-move-us-investment-bank-to-nyc_556257.html|title=UBS may move US investment bank to NYC|publisher=e-Eighteen.com Ltd|date=June 10, 2011|accessdate=March 25, 2015|archive-date=2012-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120126132835/http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/world-news/ubs-may-move-us-investment-bank-to-nyc_556257.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.longfinance.net/images/GFCI17_23March2015.pdf|title=The Global Financial Centres Index 17|date=March 23, 2015|accessdate=March 25, 2015|publisher=Long Finance|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414052808/http://www.longfinance.net/images/GFCI17_23March2015.pdf|archive-date=2015-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，紐約證券交易所也是世界市值最大的證券交易所<ref name=NYSEhighestcap>{{cite web|url=http://www.world-exchanges.org/files/2013_WFE_Market_Highlights.pdf|title=2013 WFE Market Highlights|publisher=World Federation of Exchanges|accessdate=March 25, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327112731/http://www.world-exchanges.org/files/2013_WFE_Market_Highlights.pdf|archivedate=2014年3月27日}}</ref><ref name=NYSElargest>{{cite web|url=http://www.nyse.com/about/listed/lc_ny_overview.html|title=NYSE Listings Directory|accessdate=June 23, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621174531/http://www.nyse.com/about/listed/lc_ny_overview.html|archivedate=2013年6月21日}}</ref>。金融區的範圍大致和17世紀的[[新阿姆斯特丹|新阿姆斯特丹]]重疊。近年曼哈頓金融區的人口有所增加。2014年，曼哈頓金融區大約有人口43,000人，大約是2000年23,000的近一倍<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/10/realestate/the-financial-district-gains-momentum.html?action=click&pgtype=Homepage&version=HpSectionSumSmallMedia&module=real-estate-left-region&region=real-estate-left-region&WT.nav=real-estate-left-region|title=The Financial District Gains Momentum|author=C. J. Hughes|newspaper=The New York Times|date=August 8, 2014|accessdate=August 14, 2014|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707193456/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/10/realestate/the-financial-district-gains-momentum.html?action=click&pgtype=Homepage&version=HpSectionSumSmallMedia&module=real-estate-left-region&region=real-estate-left-region&WT.nav=real-estate-left-region|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

